	  * Unbreak RGB32 fbs, where the alpha bytes ought to be ignored.
	  Happens to be the case on amdgpudrmfb
	  
	  NOTE: A cheaper workaround would be to use png_set_invert_alpha
	  But while that works for the Linux console, FBInk happily writes real
	  alpha values in there, so mixing the two doesn't work.

